title: Skrillex- Complete Discovery 2007-2013 Organized into 22 Albums
description:
This is a FULL collection of Sonny Moore's work over the years ever since he was known as "Sonny".

The following collection contains 1.64 GB (199 songs)in pure MP3s organized into 22 very clear albums/folders. These folders organize all of his released (320bit) albums, un-released songs, released singles, remixes, rips, live rips,mashups, miscellaneous etc. 

Thank you for leaving a comment if you're happy with this full discovery!
